GuideCfg.Describe: <color=#622b2b>欢迎来到我的花园！</c>
<color=#622b2b>接下来</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>点击</c></outline><color=#622b2b>关卡，开始战斗吧！</c>
<outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>长按拖动</c></outline><color=#622b2b>植物至草坪上即可放置。</c>

<color=#622b2b>放置植物会</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>消耗阳光</c></outline><color=#622b2b>以及</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>放置数量</c></outline><color=#622b2b>。</c>
<color=#622b2b>再次</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>拖动</c></outline><color=#622b2b>植物可进行进化植物进化。</c>
<color=#622b2b>进化后的植物属性将会变得更强。</c>
<color=#622b2b>坚果强可以抵御绝大部分的僵尸。</c>
<color=#622b2b>那我们就开始战斗吧！</c>
<color=#622b2b>现在让我们进行一次</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>抽奖</c></outline><color=#622b2b>。</c>
<color=#622b2b>抽取到</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>多余的碎片</c></outline><color=#622b2b>可用于升级植物。</c>
<color=#622b2b>更多植物进化路径查看图鉴！</c>
<color=#622b2b>咦?我们刚刚好像获得了一件</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>装备</c></outline><color=#622b2b>，快去看看吧！</c>

<color=#622b2b>鲍勃穿戴了</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>武器</c></outline><color=#622b2b>后，也可以在</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>出战</c></outline><color=#622b2b>了喔！</c>
<color=#622b2b>现在，装上刚刚获得的</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>武器</c></outline><color=#622b2b>试试吧！</c>
<color=#622b2b>很好，现在鲍勃也能在</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>战斗中帮忙</c></outline><color=#622b2b>了！快去试试吧！</c>
<color=#622b2b>不同的武器有不同的</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>攻击效果&冷却时间</c>

<color=#622b2b>角色下方的</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>进度条满</c></outline><color=#622b2b>后，</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>点击屏幕</c></outline><color=#622b2b>任意地方，即可痛击僵尸！</c>
现在！碾碎它们！
<color=#622b2b>听说</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>墓园抽奖</c></outline><color=#622b2b>更容易获得</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>高品质装备</c></outline>噢。</c>
<color=#622b2b>很棒！获得了新装备，别忘了</c><outline color = #3d240a width = 4><color=#46f700>穿戴</c></outline><color=#622b2b>上噢！</c>
